  messages:
  - 'Welcome to the factory floor training simulation.

    Your job is to collect
    new boxes and move them onto the grey platform.'
  - Select the toggle in the top-right of this menu to toggle tooltips on the console.
  - 'At any time, press the secondary button on your controller to reset the app.


    Good
    luck!'
